defaultQ117 default&#xa0; 
defaultChair:default Thank you very much for agreeing to give evidence on this inquiry into heat, which is proving a fascinating topic. For the record, could you introduce yourselves with your name and organisation, starting on the left?
defaultPaul Blacklockdefault: Paul Blacklock from 
defaultCalor
default Gas.
